# Local scratch work (issue tracker output; uncomment if you don't want to commit)
# .scratch/

# .scratch/ 根目录下的本地测试残留（PRD、issues、references 仍正常提交）
.scratch/req.json
.scratch/req-*.json
.scratch/server.pid
.scratch/server-test.pid

# Frontend (Next.js)
frontend/node_modules/
frontend/.next/

# Go / VS Code debug binaries
**/__debug_bin.exe
*.test.exe

# Hertz static FS compress cache (web assets use Compress: false)
*.hertz.gz
